@startuml Registration & Onboarding â€” User Level
title Registration & Onboarding

actor "New User" as user
participant "Landing Page" as landing
participant "Sign Up Page" as signup
participant "Email Inbox" as email
participant "Verify Page" as verify
participant "Org Setup Page" as orgsetup
participant "Dashboard" as dash

user -> landing : Visits cranis2.dev
user -> landing : Clicks "Get Started"
landing -> signup : Redirects to /signup

user -> signup : Enters name, email, password
user -> signup : Clicks "Create Account"
signup -> signup : Shows "Check your email" message

user -> email : Opens verification email
user -> email : Clicks verification link
email -> verify : Opens /verify-email?token=xxx

verify -> verify : Shows "Email verified!" confirmation
verify -> orgsetup : Redirects to /setup/org

user -> orgsetup : Enters organisation name
user -> orgsetup : Selects industry
user -> orgsetup : Clicks "Create Organisation"
orgsetup -> dash : Redirects to /dashboard

user -> dash : Sees dashboard with\nstat cards (all showing 0)\nand sidebar navigation
note right of dash : Onboarding complete.\nUser can now create\nproducts and connect repos.

@enduml
